title: Wednesday Post Show (08-18-21)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (08-18-21)
description:
Bobby and Caitlin celebrated their 1-month anniversary yesterday. Eddie hates on Bobby and says he’s annoying for doing that. They also watched their wedding video for the first time. Bobby also talks about getting to hang out with Jon Pardi last night. Bobby also addresses why people were going after Carrie Underwood last night.
